{"tid":2224204,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"片證女生無孭袋 飛虎被指插贓","createTime":"2020-09-30T10:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-30T11:29:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2f2963c738158df69d81e123b6795319b17bce4d","tid":2224204,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:47:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200930/B5UQNIQIDBFELDDDY6GEOJAESM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200930%2FB5UQNIQIDBFELDDDY6GEOJAESM%2F&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kynKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=dbde3cdf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200930%2FB5UQNIQIDBFELDDDY6GEOJAESM%2F&h=00bef340\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200930/B5UQNIQIDBFELDDDY6GEOJAESM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n片證女生無孭袋 飛虎被指插贓<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/y04G-gAYP5NSehZ-KXHv0D-SA0A=/1931x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FGB7MR3YEFDCRH2K7V52VHUO5A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fy04G-gAYP5NSehZ-KXHv0D-SA0A%3D%2F1931x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFGB7MR3YEFDCRH2K7V52VHUO5A.jpg&h=4919d8b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■當日中文大學附近有示威者佔據道路。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】...........................................................。辯方指他說謊及插贓嫁禍，播片證明女被告下車時根本沒孭袋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n供稱袋中搜出士巴拿<br />\n<br />\n兩被告分別為學生潘凱玲（22歲）及售貨員范瑞祐（29歲），被控在公眾地方造成阻礙罪，女生另否認管有適合作非法用途的工具並意圖作非法用途罪。<br />\n<br />\n控方傳召截停被告的兩警作供，因兩人為飛虎隊成員，身份敏感，獲准匿名以署理警長A及警長B來稱呼。<br />\n<br />\nA供稱在其中一輛貨車內發現潘，潘下車時孭着一個斜孭袋，但他沒檢查該袋。但辯方指潘的斜孭袋原放在車內，是A從車拿袋再掛在潘身上，A不同意。<br />\n<br />\n辯方隨即播放潘下車時的影片，顯示潘沒孭袋，A答鏡頭拍不到。辯方直指A說謊及插贓嫁禍，A否認。<br />\n<br />\n截停范的B稱在另一車發現范，范已被捕，他搜車時於車尾箱發現食物及水，范解釋打算分發給他人。B稱因現場危險，擔心有人搶犯，故沒警誡范，承認此舉不依程序。辯方要求剔除范的招認，認為對范不公。聆訊今續。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：STCC1095/20"},{"pid":"a0fd074d1e710722da863bb75f390e724104f035","tid":2224204,"uid":228955,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:54:03.000Z","msg":"黑警不嬲鍾意咁樣"},{"pid":"e8662b1fbe735435d8882e828ba8e5e28b07d2f8","tid":2224204,"uid":57462,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a0fd074d1e710722da863bb75f390e724104f035","tid":2224204,"uid":228955,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:54:03.000Z","msg":"黑警不嬲鍾意咁樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T11:02:10.000Z","msg":"呢d 先係真。警察通例<br />\n<br />\n由學堂開始教，前輩，同袍，上司每一個人都係咁做野<br />\n<br />\n以前淨係砌壞人咪冇人理"},{"pid":"548765ef1d3602d3a74acc57372e271e2a1cc0b4","tid":2224204,"uid":168389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T11:07:01.000Z","msg":"有睇旺角黑夜喎"},{"pid":"016f863614a30f9e49ce9be6213dc83c18c97c1c","tid":2224204,"uid":168138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T11:13:54.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">飛曱甴</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"0deed40aa8a293a59ecf7c3e6e7bd6a736e55798","tid":2224204,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8662b1fbe735435d8882e828ba8e5e28b07d2f8","tid":2224204,"uid":57462,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"a0fd074d1e710722da863bb75f390e724104f035","tid":2224204,"uid":228955,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T10:54:03.000Z","msg":"黑警不嬲鍾意咁樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T11:02:10.000Z","msg":"呢d 先係真。警察通例<br />\n<br />\n由學堂開始教，前輩，同袍，上司每一個人都係咁做野<br />\n<br />\n以前淨係砌壞人咪冇人理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T11:16:19.000Z","msg":"你肯定以前警察只屈壞人？"},{"pid":"197c02dafd9e61db781f2fca00c3d7c8e62a156f","tid":2224204,"uid":224406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T11:18:40.000Z","msg":"飛曱甴個身份有幾敏感呀<br />\n咪淨係識笠住個狗頭打學生"},{"pid":"f5cfa5092e34dddcdae9b1b707cb3347d07250b6","tid":2224204,"uid":142954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":